01:40:23.100 --> 01:40:27.900
- the next morning
I started taking the pills.

01:40:31.400 --> 01:40:35.000
How is that a compliment for me?

01:40:39.800 --> 01:40:44.900
You make me
want to be a better man.

01:40:55.200 --> 01:40:59.400
That's maybe
the best compliment of my life.

01:41:03.700 --> 01:41:09.600
Maybe I overshot a bit
to keep you from walking out.

01:41:21.300 --> 01:41:27.000
How's it going with those pills?
Good, I hope, I hope, I hope.

01:41:32.800 --> 01:41:36.100
It's little by little.

01:41:36.800 --> 01:41:42.000
It's exhausting talking like this.
Exhausting.

01:42:01.100 --> 01:42:06.000
Do you ever let a romantic moment
make you do something stupid?

01:42:06.200 --> 01:42:08.300
Never.

01:42:08.800 --> 01:42:12.000
Here's the trouble with never.

01:42:33.400 --> 01:42:38.700
- You don't owe me that.
- That wasn't payment.

01:42:39.100 --> 01:42:44.700
When I first saw you
I thought you were handsome.

01:42:45.900 --> 01:42:49.100
Then, of course, you spoke.

01:42:50.800 --> 01:42:57.100
So now that your ...
soft underbelly is all exposed ...

01:42:58.000 --> 01:43:02.400
Tell me,
why did you bring me here?

01:43:04.800 --> 01:43:06.400
Well, I ...

01:43:11.600 --> 01:43:16.900
- That's a personal question.
- Tell me, even if you're scared.

01:43:17.100 --> 01:43:21.000
- Scared?
- Tell me why you wanted me here.

01:43:21.400 --> 01:43:26.100
If you ask me, I'll say yes.

01:43:27.800 --> 01:43:29.600
I ...

01:43:31.200 --> 01:43:35.800
There's a lot of reasons.

01:43:36.500 --> 01:43:42.700
- If you had sex with Simon ...
- What?

01:43:43.600 --> 01:43:49.300
- That's just one idea.
- That's why you brought me?

01:43:49.400 --> 01:43:53.900
Like I'm a what ..?
And I owe you what?

01:43:54.000 --> 01:43:58.800
I don't know why I brought you.
It was just one thought.

01:43:58.900 --> 01:44:02.500
It came out first.

01:44:02.700 --> 01:44:06.800
You kiss him ... me ...
You two seemed to hit it off.

01:44:07.000 --> 01:44:11.700
Wait. I didn't mean ...
Forget what I said about Simon.

01:44:11.900 --> 01:44:15.600
- I'll never forget it.
- A mistake.

01:44:15.800 --> 01:44:18.200
It was a mistake.

01:44:23.800 --> 01:44:28.400
Hello, this is Fred Bishop.
We're unable to take yourcall.

01:44:28.600 --> 01:44:34.200
- Leave a message.
